{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":false,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Path2D.addPath()","mdn_url":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Path2D/addPath","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API\">Canvas API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Path2D\"><code>Path2D</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Path2D/Path2D\"><code>Path2D()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Methods</summary><ol><li><em><code>addPath()</code></em></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for Canvas API</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasGradient\"><code>CanvasGradient</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasPattern\"><code>CanvasPattern</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D\"><code>CanvasRenderingContext2D</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement\"><code>HTMLCanvasElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageBitmap\"><code>ImageBitmap</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageBitmapRenderingContext\"><code>ImageBitmapRenderingContext</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageData\"><code>ImageData</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/OffscreenCanvas\"><code>OffscreenCanvas</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextMetrics\"><code>TextMetrics</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/createImageBitmap\"><code>createImageBitmap</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>\n  The <strong><code>Path2D.addPath()</code></strong> method\n  of the Canvas 2D API adds one <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Path2D\"><code>Path2D</code></a> object to another\n  <code>Path2D</code> object.\n</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js-nolint notranslate\">addPath(path)\naddPath(path, transform)\n</pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameters","title":"Parameters","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"path\"><code>path</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>A <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Path2D\"><code>Path2D</code></a> path to add.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"transform\"><code>transform</code> <span class=\"badge inline optional\">Optional</span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>\n      A <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMMatrix\"><code>DOMMatrix</code></a> to be used as the transformation matrix for the path that\n      is added. (Technically a <code>DOMMatrixInit</code> object).\n    </p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"return_value","title":"Return value","isH3":true,"content":"<p>None (<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/undefined\"><code>undefined</code></a>).</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"Examples","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"adding_a_path_to_an_existing_path","title":"Adding a path to an existing path","isH3":true,"content":"<p>This example adds one path to another.</p>\n<h4 id=\"html\">HTML</h4>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>canvas</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>canvas<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>canvas</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"javascript\">JavaScript</h4>\n<p>\n  First, we create two separate <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Path2D\"><code>Path2D</code></a> objects, each of which contains a\n  rectangle made using the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/rect\" title=\"rect()\"><code>rect()</code></a>\n  method. We then create a matrix using <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMMatrix/DOMMatrix\" title=\"DOMMatrix()\"><code>DOMMatrix()</code></a>. We then add the second path to the first using\n  <code>addPath()</code>, also applying the matrix to move the second path to the right.\n  Finally, we draw the first path (which now contains both rectangles) using\n  <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/fill\" title=\"fill()\"><code>fill()</code></a>.\n</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> canvas <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'canvas'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> ctx <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> canvas<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getContext</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'2d'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Create first path and add a rectangle</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> p1 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Path2D</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\np1<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">rect</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">100</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">150</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Create second path and add a rectangle</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> p2 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Path2D</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\np2<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">rect</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">100</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">75</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Create transformation matrix that moves 200 points to the right</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> m <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">DOMMatrix</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nm<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>a <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> m<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>b <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nm<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>c <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> m<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>d <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nm<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>e <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">200</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> m<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>f <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Add second path to the first path</span>\np1<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addPath</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>p2<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> m<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Draw the first path</span>\nctx<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">fill</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>p1<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"result\">Result</h4><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"Adding a path to an existing path sample\" id=\"frame_adding_a_path_to_an_existing_path\" width=\"700\" height=\"180\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/en-US/docs/Web/API/Path2D/addPath/_sample_.adding_a_path_to_an_existing_path.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Specifications","id":"specifications","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/canvas.html#dom-path2d-addpath-dev","title":"HTML Standard"}],"query":"api.Path2D.addPath"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.Path2D.addPath","dataURL":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Path2D/addPath/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>The interface defining this method: <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Path2D\"><code>Path2D</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Examples","id":"examples"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"See also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"The Path2D.addPath() method\n  of the Canvas 2D API adds one Path2D object to another\n  Path2D object.","popularity":0.0004,"modified":"2022-09-13T06:09:49.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Path2D.addPath()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Path2D.addPath()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"en-us/web/api/path2d/addpath","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/blob/style/old/files/en-us/web/api/path2d/addpath/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/commit/2b8f5d9a29f00aea5d2edfa78d1fb90c51752858","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web","title":"Web technology for developers"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API","title":"Web APIs"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Path2D","title":"Path2D"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Path2D/addPath","title":"Path2D.addPath()"}],"pageTitle":"Path2D.addPath() - Web APIs | MDN","noIndexing":false}}